The paper discusses the issue of safety in the context of mobile technology and online solutions for older adults. This topic is closely related to cybersecurity (cs.CY) as well as human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also addresses real-life safety issues, which could fall under the category of security and privacy (cs.CR) or social and information networks (cs.SI). Finally, the paper proposes suggestions for improving the design of applications, which could be related to software engineering (cs.SE).
